### 配置示例 (复制到 .cursorrules)

> **Rule: Git Commit Message Protocol**
> When generating or suggesting git commit messages, strictly follow the format: `<type>: <description>`.
>
> 1. Use **Simplified Chinese** for the `<description>` and `<body>`.
> 2. Types must be one of: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, revert.
> 3. Example: `feat: 新增用户登录验证逻辑` or `fix: 修复移动端顶部导航栏遮挡问题`.
